are distraught by the withdrawal of the bare-knuckle-fighting
Giuliani. But they need not be so downcast; Lazio may have a better
chance of slaying the demon than Giuliani. For a start, Lazio will
pick up a ton of votes for the simple reason that he is not
Hillary. &QL;
