   AUTOMOTIVE NEWS
</P>
<P>
   COXNET WHEELS PAGE
</P>
<P>
   EDs: This is the CoxNet WHEELS page for the current week. This
layout is available now.
</P>
<P>
   COXNET WHEELS 0527: 2001 CHRYSLER PT CRUISER _ Looking at
Chrysler's new PT Cruiser is fun, and so is driving it. It'll make
you sit up straight, keep a grip on that billiard ball-like shift
knob and, on expressways, gravitate toward the right-hand lane.
It's not that the Cruiser won't get up and go, it's just that it
somehow feels natural to not rush when you're going somewhere in
it, which is not something said about a lot of today's vehicles
(DeVault, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art includes a 4-column
color photo of the 2001 Chrysler PT Cruiser, a 2-column color photo
of the car's front end and an 18-pica color photo of the car's
dashboard.
</P>
