u l BC-NCR-BOOK-COX     05-30 0573
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NCR-BOOK-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Recipe book serves up NCR history
 &HT;    By Laura Dempsey
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
