<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPORTS-BJT31-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE SPORTS BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These sports stories for release Wednesday, May 31, 2000, are
moving today to clients of the New York Times News Service.
</P>
