BKN-LAKERS-BLAZERS (Los Angeles) _ The Lakers and Trail Blazers
play Game 5 at Staples Center. 6 p.m. PDT. 
By Howard Beck. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BKN-CROUSE-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ Column from Lakers game. 
