is to exhibit his paintings in the Catto Gallery in Hampstead,
North London. Visitors can decide from tomorrow if the crooner
should have left his art in San Francisco.''
</P>
<P>
   _ The Daily Mail says plans are afoot for  &UR; Judi Dench &LR;  to play
novelist  &UR; Iris Murdoch &LR;  and  &UR; Michael Gambon &LR;  to play her husband,
 &UR; John Bayley &LR; , in a movie based on Bayley's book about Murdoch's
death from Alzheimer's disease.
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &UR; WHO SAID WHAT &QL;  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ``Do you have to be (messed) up to ... qualify as an &LR; 
 &UR; interesting person? And where does that leave the less fortunate &LR; 
 &UR; among us? We who have not suffered abuse; who didn't grow up in &LR; 
 &UR; some dirtball town or a soul-deading suburb? Where's our &LR; 
