<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GRAPHIC-FILES-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times News Service Macintosh
graphics files that moved Tuesday, 05/30/00. Included is the
corresponding story slug and the size. All graphics have been
posted on PressLink, NewsCom and the Wieck Photo Database.
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON_Europe visit -- 3 x 6 -- CLINTON-EUROPE
</P>
<P>
   CHINA_Yanji map -- 1 x 2 1/4 -- CHINA-NKOREA
</P>
<P>
   LEBANON_Bint Jbail map -- 1 x 2 1/2 -- LEBANON-HEZBOLLAH
</P>
<P>
   ENGLAND_Great Brington -- 1 x 2 1/2 -- ENGLAND-ALTHORP
</P>
<P>
   YUGOSLAVIA_Kragujevac map -- 1 x 3 -- YUGOSLAVIA-KRAGUJEVAC
